250
00:21:09,949 --> 00:21:11,309
No.

251
00:21:11,310 --> 00:21:13,829
- You scared the hell out of me.
- Hello, is this 120?

252
00:21:13,829 --> 00:21:15,760
- This… This is—
- Miss Chen.

253
00:21:17,030 --> 00:21:18,759
She came around. Sorry, we no longer have such a need.

254
00:21:18,759 --> 00:21:21,129
All right, okay, all right. Thanks.

255
00:21:21,779 --> 00:21:23,629
Do you feel any better?

256
00:21:26,660 --> 00:21:27,980
Aren't you…

257
00:21:27,980 --> 00:21:31,009
I'm Qian Kaiyi. You Na's substitute teacher.

258
00:21:31,009 --> 00:21:32,760
I answered your call the other day.

259
00:21:32,760 --> 00:21:36,029
Sorry, Miss He. It's all my fault.

260
00:21:42,630 --> 00:21:44,550
You Na's mother!

261
00:21:45,210 --> 00:21:48,709
Please rest assured that the school will do its best to cooperate with the investigation.

262
00:21:48,709 --> 00:21:51,999
Miss Chen, it's not that I'm intent on making trouble for you today.

263
00:21:51,999 --> 00:21:54,393
Such a big thing happened, one after another.

264
00:21:54,393 --> 00:21:57,339
This is a child who's about to take the college entrance exam. She can't stand such screwups.

265
00:21:57,339 --> 00:21:58,892
Yes, yes, yes.

266
00:21:58,893 --> 00:22:01,289
But at first, we arranged art classes

267
00:22:01,289 --> 00:22:03,729
with the intention of balancing the children's grades in academic subjects.

268
00:22:03,729 --> 00:22:06,641
To save them from running between two places, we provide a free venue.

269
00:22:06,641 --> 00:22:08,410
We didn't expect it'd cause so many accidents.

270
00:22:08,410 --> 00:22:09,779
- It's indeed our inconsiderateness—
- Forget it.

271
00:22:09,779 --> 00:22:12,829
You Na's mother, let's have a word in private.

272
00:22:12,829 --> 00:22:15,200
It's all right. Just say it here if you've got anything to say.

273
00:22:15,200 --> 00:22:18,059
Today, the school's counseling office did an assessment on You Na.

274
00:22:18,059 --> 00:22:22,429
Their preliminary suggestion is to let You Na go through professional psychotherapy.

275
00:22:22,429 --> 00:22:25,719
Is that necessary? I brought Na Na up since she was a baby.

276
00:22:25,719 --> 00:22:28,339
If you really challenge her to jump to her death, she wouldn't dare.

277
00:22:28,339 --> 00:22:31,410
- But today she has twice—
- You Na's mother,

278
00:22:31,410 --> 00:22:36,529
if you have any need for psychological counseling later, you can contact me through the school's teacher.

279
00:22:36,529 --> 00:22:39,190
Of course, I hope you won't need it.

280
00:22:39,190 --> 00:22:40,660
Thank you.

281
00:22:40,660 --> 00:22:42,989
Miss Chen. No matter what happens,

282
00:22:42,989 --> 00:22:45,270
I hope you can give me an explanation as soon as possible and give Na Na an explanation as well.

283
00:22:45,270 --> 00:22:46,180
Yes, yes, yes.

284
00:22:46,180 --> 00:22:49,219
- Otherwise, I'll certainly talk to Director Wu of the Education Bureau—
- Na Na!

285
00:22:50,510 --> 00:22:52,030
Dad.

286
00:22:59,737 --> 00:23:01,427
Are you all right?

287
00:23:04,200 --> 00:23:06,120
Sorry, I'm late.

288
00:23:07,452 --> 00:23:12,700
Well, s-sorry to bring you guys trouble with what happened to Na Na today.

289
00:23:14,200 --> 00:23:18,829
By the way, I think it's quite normal for children to have a quarrel.

290
00:23:18,829 --> 00:23:21,520
Don't be hard on the other child as well.

291
00:23:21,520 --> 00:23:25,629
- After all, they are about to take the college entrance exam, and they—
- Na Na!

292
00:23:25,629 --> 00:23:27,280
Na Na!

293
00:23:29,260 --> 00:23:31,940
- You'd better care about your own daughter in the first place.
- Na Na!

294
00:23:31,940 --> 00:23:34,440
You Na's mother, please wait a minute.

295
00:23:37,990 --> 00:23:41,829
You Na's mother, can I have a word with you?

296
00:23:43,670 --> 00:23:46,639
Look at this. This is a photo provided by Mr. Qian.

297
00:23:46,639 --> 00:23:49,660
It's a photo of You Na taken by other students.

298
00:23:49,660 --> 00:23:53,519
Actually, before you and the police arrived, I had persuaded her to come down.

299
00:23:53,519 --> 00:23:56,279
But it doesn't mean the situation at that time was not dangerous,

300
00:23:56,279 --> 00:24:00,119
nor does it mean she didn't want to jump or dared not jump.

301
00:24:00,119 --> 00:24:03,140
That is totally different from what happened in the indoor swimming pool today in nature.

302
00:24:03,140 --> 00:24:05,599
Besides, I've only solved her current crisis.

303
00:24:05,600 --> 00:24:09,059
I can't guarantee she won't have such thoughts in the coming days.

304
00:24:09,059 --> 00:24:12,639
So make sure to keep an eye on what she'll be doing when at home.

305
00:24:14,550 --> 00:24:17,129
All right. I got it.

306
00:24:19,430 --> 00:24:23,299
If it's convenient, could I also have a word with You Na?

307
00:24:23,299 --> 00:24:25,060
Sure.

308
00:24:25,060 --> 00:24:26,560
Thanks.

309
00:24:28,916 --> 00:24:30,406
You Na.

310
00:24:31,376 --> 00:24:33,536
Can I ask you a question?

311
00:24:35,360 --> 00:24:40,090
How did you know I am the operator who answered your call to the Suicide Intervention Center?

312
00:24:40,689 --> 00:24:43,709
You have a nice voice. I'm studying broadcasting and hosting.

313
00:24:43,709 --> 00:24:47,119
I'm sensitive to voices and remember yours after listening to it once.

314
00:24:49,240 --> 00:24:50,790
I see.

315
00:24:50,790 --> 00:24:54,229
Go home early to change your clothes. In case you catch a cold.

316
00:24:58,690 --> 00:25:02,289
Thank you for what you did today. We are going for now.

317
00:25:18,000 --> 00:25:20,749
Miss He, thank you for coming to the school today.

318
00:25:20,749 --> 00:25:24,969
Had you not saved You Na in time, we'd have to take a bigger share of responsibility.

319
00:25:24,969 --> 00:25:28,940
Don't mention it. I was just doing something as my capacity allows.

320
00:25:28,940 --> 00:25:33,180
As your capacity allows? You almost lost your breath.

321
00:25:33,180 --> 00:25:37,799
Yes, yes, yes. Also thank you to Mr. Kaiyi for showing up in time to save Miss He.

322
00:25:37,799 --> 00:25:39,760
That's what I should do.

323
00:25:39,760 --> 00:25:41,720
I'm going for now if there's nothing left for me.

324
00:25:41,720 --> 00:25:45,459
Don't rush. It's so dark at night. Where are you going to find a car?

325
00:25:46,440 --> 00:25:47,929
Let me give you a ride home on my motorbike.

326
00:25:47,930 --> 00:25:51,259
No, thanks. My friend is waiting for me.

327
00:25:54,110 --> 00:25:57,129
Go. This is not the only thing you owe me anyway.

328
00:25:57,129 --> 00:25:59,980
Mr. Qian, Miss He, you guys are wet.

329
00:25:59,980 --> 00:26:02,899
If you ride a motorbike all the way home, you'll certainly catch a cold.

330
00:26:02,899 --> 00:26:07,649
I have a couple of brand new school uniforms with me. Why don't you wear them for now?

