Are you good at riding or not?

343
00:27:59,040 --> 00:28:01,520
I asked whether you can do it or not.

344
00:28:01,520 --> 00:28:04,829
You must be kidding. Have you heard of God of Motor Racing on Qiuming Mountain?

345
00:28:04,829 --> 00:28:06,140
What mountain?

346
00:28:06,140 --> 00:28:10,140
God of Motor Racing on Qiuming Mountain.

347
00:28:10,140 --> 00:28:13,329
God of Motor Racing on Qiuming Mountain, pull off the road. Pull off the road.

348
00:28:13,329 --> 00:28:16,910
Did you hear me? God of Motor Racing on Qiuming Mountain, please pull off the road.

349
00:28:16,910 --> 00:28:19,900
[Profile of Anchorman Qian Kaiyi]

350
00:28:24,160 --> 00:28:26,410
Is this you?

351
00:28:26,410 --> 00:28:30,320
Sir, this is me indeed. My ID is soaked in water.

352
00:28:30,320 --> 00:28:31,540
And she didn't even bring hers.

353
00:28:31,540 --> 00:28:33,050
Yes, sir.

354
00:28:33,050 --> 00:28:35,109
If you don't believe him, you can believe me.

355
00:28:35,109 --> 00:28:37,450
What he said just now is all true.

356
00:28:39,830 --> 00:28:42,080
You kids, don't do this with me.

357
00:28:42,080 --> 00:28:45,280
Instead of sleeping at home at night, you sneaked out for a date

358
00:28:45,280 --> 00:28:47,779
and don't focus your mind on schoolwork.

359
00:28:47,779 --> 00:28:51,325
We've caught two high school students. Underage people driving a motor vehicle.

360
00:28:51,325 --> 00:28:53,550
We are going to take them back now.

361
00:28:53,550 --> 00:28:56,779
I've got you guys. God of Motor Racing on Qiuming Mountain.

362
00:28:56,779 --> 00:28:59,070
- Take them away.
- All right.

363
00:28:59,070 --> 00:29:01,020
Go with me, guys.

364
00:29:02,210 --> 00:29:03,880
God of Motor Racing on Qiuming Mountain.

365
00:29:03,880 --> 00:29:05,420
Go.

366
00:29:59,500 --> 00:30:00,380
He Dun.

367
00:30:03,370 --> 00:30:06,399
- Lili. You've come to get me out.
- What was going on?

368
00:30:06,399 --> 00:30:08,000
Sister.

369
00:30:09,640 --> 00:30:11,740
What are you guys doing?

370
00:30:13,310 --> 00:30:14,999
- Who's their family member?
- Me.

371
00:30:14,999 --> 00:30:16,279
Come in to sign your names.

372
00:30:16,279 --> 00:30:18,449
Hello, sir. I'm his colleague.

373
00:30:18,449 --> 00:30:22,299
This is Qian Kaiyi, announcer of Haifeng Radio International.

374
00:30:22,910 --> 00:30:25,039
Sir, I'm her friend.

375
00:30:25,039 --> 00:30:27,810
This is psychological counselor He Dun.

376
00:30:31,930 --> 00:30:34,819
All right. Come in to sign your names.

377
00:30:42,380 --> 00:30:44,400
Aren't you a teacher?

378
00:30:45,350 --> 00:30:46,970
A part-time one.

379
00:30:59,420 --> 00:31:02,729
Actually, before you and the police arrived, I had persuaded her to come down.

380
00:31:02,729 --> 00:31:05,339
But it doesn't mean the situation at that time was not dangerous,

381
00:31:05,339 --> 00:31:09,250
nor does it mean she didn't want to jump or dared not jump.

382
00:31:09,250 --> 00:31:11,820
That is totally different from what happened in the indoor swimming pool today in nature.

383
00:31:11,820 --> 00:31:14,279
Besides, I've only solved her current crisis.

384
00:31:14,279 --> 00:31:18,159
I can't guarantee she won't have such thought in the coming days.

385
00:31:28,100 --> 00:31:29,470
Good for you.

386
00:31:29,470 --> 00:31:32,059
You left me in the middle of the night and went for cosplay with others.

387
00:31:32,059 --> 00:31:33,809
I'll tell you about it later.

388
00:31:33,810 --> 00:31:35,580
Hello, I'm Tang Lili.

389
00:31:35,580 --> 00:31:37,180
I'm Xiong Qiao.

390
00:31:39,020 --> 00:31:41,110
By the way, I forgot to introduce myself.

391
00:31:41,110 --> 00:31:42,260
I'm Qian Kaiyi.

392
00:31:42,260 --> 00:31:45,180
I'm an anchor of Haifeng Radio International.

393
00:31:46,350 --> 00:31:48,520
You've introduced yourself just now.

394
00:31:49,900 --> 00:31:51,329
Would you like me to give you a ride?

395
00:31:51,330 --> 00:31:54,019
No, thanks. My friend drove her car here.

396
00:31:54,860 --> 00:31:55,990
What about you?

397
00:31:55,990 --> 00:31:57,109
No need, thanks.

398
00:31:57,109 --> 00:31:59,190
Don't forget about your proper business.

399
00:32:02,290 --> 00:32:03,920
Thank you, Sister.

400
00:32:04,570 --> 00:32:06,750
- Let's go too.
- All right.

401
00:32:07,620 --> 00:32:09,279
Come to think of it, well,

402
00:32:09,279 --> 00:32:13,259
my colleague asked me if you know any professional psychological counselors.

403
00:32:13,259 --> 00:32:14,759
She'd like to have psychological counseling.

404
00:32:14,759 --> 00:32:17,260
Miss He, can you do that?

405
00:32:18,070 --> 00:32:20,400
A psychological counseling session needs to be done in a professional counseling office.

406
00:32:20,400 --> 00:32:23,839
I've left Yunkai. I can't do it at the moment.

407
00:32:24,570 --> 00:32:28,039
By the way, please leave your contact number.

408
00:32:29,400 --> 00:32:32,899
Didn't you say I can contact you if You Na's mother needs any help?

409
00:32:32,899 --> 00:32:35,160
We don't have each other's contact number.

410
00:32:36,500 --> 00:32:38,070
Your cellphone.

411
00:32:52,110 --> 00:32:54,000
Thanks.

412
00:32:54,000 --> 00:32:55,800
We are going then.

413
00:32:57,900 --> 00:32:59,630
Bye.

414
00:33:11,280 --> 00:33:14,409
Careful. Put it over there.

415
00:33:17,230 --> 00:33:19,160
Yes, put it over there.

416
00:33:19,710 --> 00:33:21,190
Be careful, okay?

417
00:33:21,190 --> 00:33:23,850
Yes, put it over there. Thanks.

418
00:33:24,470 --> 00:33:27,290
- Lili.
- You've got up.

419
00:33:27,290 --> 00:33:29,699
- Isn't this my dormitory painting?
- Yes.

420
00:33:29,699 --> 00:33:33,310
These boxes and these clothes are all yours.

421
00:33:34,280 --> 00:33:37,190
Why? Are you afraid I'm doing charity by taking you in?

422
00:33:37,190 --> 00:33:39,770
Let's make an oral agreement first. We'll split the rent.

423
00:33:39,770 --> 00:33:42,729
- Well…
- Don't worry. I won't drop anything.

424
00:33:42,729 --> 00:33:45,689
I've even packed the trash in your trash can for you.

425
00:33:45,689 --> 00:33:48,620
And there's also a mysterious guest.

426
00:33:52,680 --> 00:33:54,590
How could you ask Qian Kaiyi to come over to help?

427
00:33:54,590 --> 00:33:57,470
- How did you know?
- Of course, I know.

428
00:33:58,110 --> 00:34:01,649
Miss Dior Cherie Blooming Bouquet. I love this perfume too.

429
00:34:02,980 --> 00:34:04,830
Your express delivery is here.

430
00:34:08,870 --> 00:34:12,719
Could this box of Gundam models be wrongly delivered by the home-moving company?

431
00:34:17,490 --> 00:34:18,930
Hello, Miss Dior.

432
00:34:18,930 --> 00:34:20,810
Mr. Qian.

433
00:34:20,810 --> 00:34:23,900
I'm not the Miss Dior today.

434
00:34:24,620 --> 00:34:26,050
I've smelt it.

435
00:34:27,980 --> 00:34:30,710
Why did you ask him to come over to help?

436
00:34:30,710 --> 00:34:32,180
He said he was coming to ask you for help.

437
00:34:32,180 --> 00:34:35,249
I said although He Dun is kind-hearted, she can't help you for nothing.

438
00:34:35,249 --> 00:34:38,010
- Even so you can't…
- All right, all right.

439
00:34:38,010 --> 00:34:40,180
I've got your SIM card changed.

440
00:34:41,380 --> 00:34:44,790
I've been busy all day, only to get not a word of thanks from someone.

441
00:34:46,760 --> 00:34:50,549
Stop, stop. I was kidding you. We are besties.

442
00:34:50,549 --> 00:34:52,970
I'm not thanking you. I'm worshipping you.

443
00:34:52,970 --> 00:34:56,229
Sure enough, a top-level executive secretary is quite something.

444
00:34:56,229 --> 00:34:59,260
Everything I can and can't think of, you've got it ready for me beforehand.

445
00:34:59,260 --> 00:35:02,259
We will be cohabiting from now on.

446
00:35:02,259 --> 00:35:05,080
I'll certainly wait on you hand and foot in the coming days.

447
00:35:05,080 --> 00:35:07,730
Yes. So will my good life begin?

448
00:35:10,970 --> 00:35:13,719
Will it be over after this round of moving?

449
00:35:13,719 --> 00:35:15,990
Just leave it. Thank you, Mr. Qian.

450
00:35:15,990 --> 00:35:17,810
Didn't you say you have something to ask for He Dun's help?

451
00:35:17,810 --> 00:35:21,989
To be exact, it's not me. It's You Na's mother.

452
00:35:45,380 --> 00:35:46,910
Na Na…

453
00:35:47,620 --> 00:35:49,139
Na Na…

454
00:35:49,140 --> 00:35:50,419
Mom...

455
00:35:50,420 --> 00:35:54,669
Na Na… It's all right. I'm here.

456
00:35:54,669 --> 00:35:57,810
It's all right. It's all right.

457
00:35:57,810 --> 00:35:59,320
It's all right.

458
00:36:31,220 --> 00:36:34,259
Miss He. Why must it be done in a counseling office?

459
00:36:34,259 --> 00:36:37,670
Can't we find a quiet cafe as a workaround?

460
00:36:37,670 --> 00:36:40,689
Just now You Na's mother called me and she was distraught.

461
00:36:40,689 --> 00:36:42,999
I don't think she would mind such a problem.

462
00:36:42,999 --> 00:36:45,929
Shall I give her a call and communicate in advance?

463
00:36:45,929 --> 00:36:49,879
You Na's mother prefers a face-to-face psychological counseling session.

464
00:36:49,879 --> 00:36:52,669
And now You Na only accepts your help.

465
00:36:52,669 --> 00:36:55,359
Or we can find a VIP booth.

466
00:36:55,359 --> 00:36:57,319
Isn't it just as quiet and with no disturbance?

467
00:36:57,319 --> 00:37:00,479
Generally speaking, that is not allowed by the setting principle of counseling.

468
00:37:00,479 --> 00:37:05,609
The surroundings for counseling entail a fixed place, a fixed frequency, and a fixed time.

469
00:37:05,609 --> 00:37:09,580
Once the place changes back and forth, there would be a lot of uncontrollable factors.

470
00:37:09,580 --> 00:37:11,670
Visitors would also have to adapt frequently.

471
00:37:11,670 --> 00:37:14,629
They would become anxious, uneasy, and have no sense of security,

472
00:37:14,629 --> 00:37:17,590
which is not a good thing for counseling.

473
00:37:18,290 --> 00:37:19,840
I've suddenly come to think of something.

474
00:37:19,840 --> 00:37:24,190
Didn't you save a sum of money to open an individual practice office?

475
00:37:24,190 --> 00:37:26,779
You even got the license, but Mr. Wang made you stay.

476
00:37:26,779 --> 00:37:28,359
Isn't this a good opportunity?

477
00:37:28,359 --> 00:37:29,869
I've just quit my job.

478
00:37:29,869 --> 00:37:31,709
I haven't found a new workplace yet.

479
00:37:31,709 --> 00:37:33,420
It's too hasty.

480
00:37:34,620 --> 00:37:37,089
I think we can just vacate the living room on the first floor.

481
00:37:37,089 --> 00:37:40,519
Anyway, I'm at work during the day and not at home. You can run your business.

482
00:37:40,519 --> 00:37:41,709
Just in time.

483
00:37:41,709 --> 00:37:43,769
But I just don't know if the space is big enough.

484
00:37:43,769 --> 00:37:44,999
The space is big enough for sure.

485
00:37:44,999 --> 00:37:47,879
Generally speaking, a counseling office only needs 10 to 12 square meters.

486
00:37:47,879 --> 00:37:50,209
If it's too big, it'll make people feel insecure.

487
00:37:50,209 --> 00:37:52,450
If it's too small, it'll make people feel oppressive.

488
00:37:52,450 --> 00:37:55,069
But this is too hasty for me.

489
00:37:55,069 --> 00:37:57,600
I haven't figured it out yet.

490
00:37:57,600 --> 00:38:00,190
Well, what else do you need to prepare?

491
00:38:00,190 --> 00:38:04,929
Do you think any room can be a counseling office?

